{"title":"Hands-on with Frosthaven’s ambitious port from gigantic box to inviting PC game","link":"https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2025/03/frosthavens-weighty-tabletop-tactics-are-coming-to-pc-in-early-access-this-year/","date":1742505524000,"content":"<p><em>Frosthaven</em>, a board game that was somehow <a href=\"https://www.ign.com/articles/frosthaven-board-game-review\">even bigger</a> and more ambitious than its <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2017/04/gloomhaven-review-2017s-biggest-board-game-is-astoundingly-good/\">considerably weighty forebear <em>Gloomhaven</em></a>, asks a lot of its players.</p>\n<p>Each turn means picking two from maybe a dozen different possible action cards. Each of those cards has two options (plus a \"default\"), and each of those cards is played out against multiple other actions by your enemies and companions. And that's just the game itself—actually getting the game set up and getting your fellow gamers to agree on semi-regular appointments is a whole other crusade against tough odds.</p>\n<figure>\n      <img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large-1024x576.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large-640x360.jpeg 640w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large-384x216.jpeg 384w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large-1152x648.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large-980x551.jpeg 980w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_MetallicRuins_Scenario_Screenshot_03-Large.jpeg 1280w\" />\n      <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <div></div>\n    <div>\n      When you're zoomed in, and especially in interior spaces, you can easily see <em>Frosthaven</em>'s hex-based board game roots\n\n              <span>\n          Credit:\n\n          \n          Arc Games\n\n                  </span>\n          </div>\n  </div>\n      </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n      <figure>\n      <img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large-1024x576.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large-640x360.jpeg 640w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large-384x216.jpeg 384w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large-1152x648.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large-980x551.jpeg 980w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Vault_Scenario_Screenshot-Large.jpeg 1280w\" />\n      <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <div></div>\n    <div>\n      Treacherous terrain is a big part of the strategy, whether using it for power-ups or kiting enemies into bad spots.\n\n              <span>\n          Credit:\n\n          \n          Arc Games\n\n                  </span>\n          </div>\n  </div>\n      </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n      <figure>\n      <img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large-1024x576.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large-640x360.jpeg 640w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large-384x216.jpeg 384w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large-1152x648.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large-980x551.jpeg 980w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_AnnounceTrailer_Screenshot_02-Large.jpeg 1280w\" />\n      <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <div></div>\n    <div>\n      Summons and spell-casting add another layer of complexity onto the game's meaty combat.\n\n              <span>\n          Credit:\n\n          \n          Arc Games\n\n                  </span>\n          </div>\n  </div>\n      </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n      <figure>\n      <img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large-1024x576.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large-640x360.jpeg 640w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large-384x216.jpeg 384w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large-1152x648.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large-980x551.jpeg 980w, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frosthaven_Outpost_Evolved_Winter_Screenshot-Large.jpeg 1280w\" />\n      <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <div></div>\n    <div>\n      Your outpost provides you with boons, quests, and other higher-level management options.\n\n              <span>\n          Credit:\n\n          \n          Arc Games\n\n                  </span>\n          </div>\n  </div>\n      </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n  \n<p>Like <em>Gloomhaven </em>before it, <em>Frosthaven</em> is getting a PC game, which should make exploring a baddie-infested tundra easier to set up and potentially easier to do multiplayer. A closed beta test begins March 27, with <a href=\"https://playfrosthaven.com/\">sign-ups at the game's website</a>. The game will launch into early access during 2025, with more than 35 quests across the first two acts available, with over 130 quests planned in total. It will have single-player and up to four-player multiplayer, with players able to pick up their teammates' characters if there's a momentary dropout.</p><p><a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2025/03/frosthavens-weighty-tabletop-tactics-are-coming-to-pc-in-early-access-this-year/\">Read full article</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2025/03/frosthavens-weighty-tabletop-tactics-are-coming-to-pc-in-early-access-this-year/#comments\">Comments</a></p>","author":"Kevin Purdy","siteTitle":"Ars Technica","siteHash":"5b0ddf6e8923e49262a7894cfd77962733e43fbcc565a103b48373820b310636","entryHash":"e021aa5380e4f614d4660b90c63ea379f4483cc3e05ba817657b9fb495f2b931","category":"Tech"}